data.description: Get away from the hustle and bustle of town and take a look at this charming 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home situated on over half an acre right outside of the city limits! No city property taxes! The copper metal roof adds to the curb appeal! Home offers an open concept floor plan. The extra large formal dining room includes a wet bar with a sink. Great for entertaining! The primary bedroom has a large walk in closet while the primary bathroom includes dual sinks, lighted vanity, a tiled walk in shower, and a jetted tub! There is a bonus room that could be used as an office, gym, craft room, etc. It is currently being used as a fourth bedroom. The jack and jill guest bathroom offers separate vanities and toilets with a shared tub-shower combo. Relax in your large back yard with shade trees and a nice view! There is also a workshop with electricity! Home also includes a chemical free water filtration system that is owned and will convey. New exterior AC installed on 8-18-2023!
